data.description: Welcome Home to Elegance and Comfort in the Heart of Winter Haven, FL. Nestled on an expansive half-acre corner lot, this single-story single family home epitomizes the perfect blend of luxury and comfort, located in the esteemed Cypresswood gated community, where a 24-hour security guard ensures your peace of mind. As you enter, you're embraced by the inviting allure of this home, where every detail has been carefully considered. The heart of the home is a spacious living room, complete with a cozy fireplace, offering the ideal setting for intimate gatherings or relaxed evenings. The kitchen is a culinary haven, boasting generous counter space and cabinetry. With room for a small table, it's the perfect spot for casual meals and conversations, making every mealtime a delight. For more formal occasions, the separate dining room provides an elegant space to host family and friends, ensuring cherished memories are created. Additionally, a second living area lends versatility to your lifestyle, serving as a home office, entertainment zone, or simply a place for relaxation. Step outside to your private screened-in pool area, where you can revel in the Florida sunshine, enjoy a refreshing swim, and entertain in style. The outdoor space is further enhanced by the lush landscaping that surrounds the property, creating a tranquil and secluded haven. Unique to this home is the expansive washer and dryer room with ample storage, making the chore of laundry a breeze and providing much-needed convenience. But there's more to discover beyond your doorstep. The Cypresswood subdivision is home to an 18-hole golf course, a haven for golf aficionados. The clubhouse is a hub of social activity, housing a restaurant and bar, making it an ideal place to unwind and connect with neighbors and fellow residents. This property offers a rare combination of opulence and functionality in a vibrant, secure community. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional home yours! ***Owner is also including a home warranty & $5K towards closing cost***    3D Virtual Tour Link - https://tour.vht.com/434344409/2901-plantation-road-winter-haven-fl-33884/3dtour
